{"tid":1775432,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣短片］向前線抗爭者致敬","createTime":"2019-12-09T00:32:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T07:50:09.000Z","uid":343390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6b6fd7ee7fbf83f35799a361169bd441667a9064","tid":1775432,"uid":343390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T00:32:29.000Z","msg":"巴絲手足<br />\n<br />\n小弟要講對唔住，呢幾個月除咗出過去一次之外都因為家庭關係出唔到嚟幫手，只可以做鍵盤戰士<br />\n<br />\n咁啱緊排初學剪輯，於是自己上網搵返啲之前睇直播嘅片，再搵多少少片，剪咗一條又唔係微電影又唔係紀錄片嘅。。。總之係短片啦，紀念六週月前線嘅堅持同付出，同埋希望有故事性咁share俾外國朋友<br />\n<br />\n啲片基本上都係呢個月上網搵新聞片二次創作，所以有啲都幾矇，同埋新手第一次剪重有好多要改善嘅空間，希望大家唔好咁大力插<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AMcsOBnBbDY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAMcsOBnBbDY&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2LdfY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=6d0e7a3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AMcsOBnBbDY</a>"},{"pid":"4b7149c45c38254e4d02ef462f75725ca0724f8c","tid":1775432,"uid":343390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T03:35:19.000Z","msg":"　"},{"pid":"f19d81f7b97575d7459bfa228352f7bb1a6d3d84","tid":1775432,"uid":343390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T03:36:47.000Z","msg":"　"},{"pid":"e3f1e1874fa0ddf309fc180f88b5a6a0b54348ec","tid":1775432,"uid":343390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T03:42:59.000Z","msg":"　"},{"pid":"803655430772bd31712ee429df1f7cb21078cd4c","tid":1775432,"uid":343390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T07:50:09.000Z","msg":"啱啱發現俾YouTube mark咗限制級，但其實入面嘅暴力片段都係黑警同黑社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}